title: Is anyone else not getting the " go SSW and  Go SSG" Missions?
body: I know they realise missions per week for worlds but these 2 (Which from my understanding were to be released week 1 of worlds) haven't appeared in my mission list. I've done the others like Go Fnatic and etc but its just these 2 that haven't appeared for me. Am i missing something or is there a bug?

replies.body:
They release on the 5th (SSG) and 6th (SSW). You can find specifics (including dates) for the missions here:
https://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/special-event/learn-more-worlds-season-2018-event#faq
